BT 1 0 0 1 0 50 Tm .132006 Tw 12 TL /F1 10 Tf 0 0 0 rg (We discussed supervised and unsupervised learning in the ) Tj (Define Goals and Metrics) Tj ( section. If you are dealing with) Tj T* 0 Tw -0.105519 Tw (a supervised learning problem \(as is likely\), the largest concern of data collection is how the data can be labeled. In a) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.914116 Tw (supervised learning application, we want to learn to predict some quantity from our data. To do that, we need) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.049116 Tw (examples which match our data and that quantity together. For example if we want an AI application that detects) Tj T* 0 Tw (spam, we need to collect as data a set of emails, and divide them up into two categories - spam or not.) Tj T* ET
