BT 1 0 0 1 0 62 Tm /F1 10 Tf 12 TL .147584 Tw (Fundamentally, you have two choices of how to do this. Firstly, you can contrive a way to achieve this automatically.) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.191624 Tw (If you are predicting how sales from your website occur based on how people engage with it, it might be a fairly) Tj T* 0 Tw .080671 Tw (simple affair for you to match these two bits of information up. Otherwise, if you can\222t contrive a way to do otherwise,) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.694705 Tw (the data must be labeled manually, by hand. For example, in a dataset of pictures of animals, the only way to) Tj T* 0 Tw .266265 Tw (effectively know what animal is present in the picture is to get a human to decide. In general, we wish to avoid this -) Tj T* 0 Tw (for the purposes of this type of task, humans are expensive, prone to error and hard to scale.) Tj T* ET
Q
Q
