BT 1 0 0 1 0 62 Tm /F1 10 Tf 12 TL .160195 Tw (Other than this, the process of how you will collect your data is simply the practical realization of what you\222ve set out) Tj T* 0 Tw .056705 Tw (in the previous steps. Your focus here is making the process as simple and replicable as possible. As a general rule,) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.703606 Tw (the more automated the process can be, the better. Automated collection processes scale better, and involving) Tj T* 0 Tw .989116 Tw (human factors in the collection process is usually an excellent way to introduce an extra set of errors. Automated) Tj T* 0 Tw 2.129116 Tw (data collection isn\222t possible in every application though. If you do have to have people involved in your data) Tj T* 0 Tw (collection process, try and work as hard as you can to maximize the consistency of the process for them.) Tj T* ET
