BT 1 0 0 1 0 38 Tm /F1 10 Tf 12 TL .487756 Tw (Compared to many software engineering projects, AI projects can often suffer from large variances in behavior due) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.024426 Tw (to the stochastic nature of the algorithms involved. A consequence of this is that it is imperative to maintain clear) Tj T* 0 Tw .519606 Tw (documentation. We must be able to clearly distinguish between acceptable variances in behavior due to irreducible) Tj T* 0 Tw (randomness in our processes, and unacceptable variances in behavior due to mistakes.) Tj T* ET
