BT 1 0 0 1 0 26 Tm .803561 Tw 12 TL /F2 10 Tf 0 0 0 rg (How you collected it) Tj /F1 10 Tf (. A good description should both include a succinct high level description of what was done,) Tj T* 0 Tw .132006 Tw (and include enough detail to allow a full replication. Especially for complicated data collection paradigms, the devil is) Tj T* 0 Tw (often in the details, and seemingly unimportant details can become important later.) Tj T* ET
Q
Q
