1 0 0 1 40.01575 119.0394 cm
q
BT 1 0 0 1 0 26 Tm .918205 Tw 12 TL /F2 10 Tf 0 0 0 rg (Why you did it this way) Tj /F1 10 Tf (. Should both rationalize the process you took and, crucially, why you did this instead of) Tj T* 0 Tw .278561 Tw (other things. This gives important contextual hints to anyone trying to replicate your results that may be absent from) Tj T* 0 Tw (a pure \223how\224 description, and can help them avoid any problems you encountered in the process.) Tj T* ET
